TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.DSPN_DT, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.EXTL_SRC_CD, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.CLM_TYP_CD, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.PRD_ID, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.RBEL_CLNT_CD, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.RBAT_ID, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.LCM_CD, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.EXTL_LVL1_ID, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.EXTL_LVL2_ID, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.EXTL_LVL3_ID, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.EXTL_LVL4_ID, VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.EXTL_LVL5_ID FROM VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV, VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS WHERE --Filters VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.INV_ELIG_DT BETWEEN $$MIN_MTH_STRT_DT AND $$HOLD_END_DT AND VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.PRD_ID = $$HOLD_PRD_ID -- hold periods AND VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.MODEL_TYP_CD = 'H' AND --Joins VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.PRD_ID = VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.PRD_ID
AND VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.MODEL_TYP_CD = VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.MODEL_TYP_CD --

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: User Defined Join
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
--Joins Not used anymore, see SQL override VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.PRD_ID = VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.PRD_ID
AND VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.MODEL_TYP_CD = VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.MODEL_TYP_CD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Source Filter
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: --Filters Not used anymore, see SQL override VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.INV_ELIG_DT BETWEEN $$MIN_MTH_STRT_DT AND $$HOLD_END_DT AND ((VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.CLM_LOCK_CD in ($$CLM_LOCK_CD) -- Closed or Open periods AND VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.APC_STAT_CD IN ($$APC_STAT_CD)) -- APC is open OR VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.PRD_ID = $$HOLD_PRD_ID) -- hold periods
